0.02 - 2013-02-24   (Alexis Sukrieh)

    [ DOCUMENTATION ]
    * No more "TODO" tokens in the documentations
    * More documentation for Core classes
    (Alexis Sukrieh)

    [ ENHANCEMENTS ]
